             was indicted for <rs id="t18311201-285-off1515" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18311201-285-off1515" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18311201-285-off1515" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18311201-285-cd1516" type="crimeDate">30th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311201-285-off1515 t18311201-285-cd1516"></join>, 3 spoons, value 20s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18311201-285-victim2136" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Lawrence
               <interp inst="t18311201-285-victim2136" type="surname" value="Lawrence"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18311201-285-victim2136" type="given" value="William"></interp>
